Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:08.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.67,0:01:10.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is even cooler than Ginza Kami-Sakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:15.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's all I know. I really have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.12,0:01:17.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are a dozen other dangerous folks around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.78,0:01:18.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you'd better watch out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.74,0:01:22.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you saw that black bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:24.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't had such a sweet deal for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.35,0:01:25.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's fucking jailbait.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.89,0:01:27.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Props to the informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.07,0:01:32.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment I noticed that I was trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:04.61,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the reality you perceive "real"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.31,0:02:08.32,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The familiar scenery is still the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.84,0:02:13.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to congratulate everyone on their admittance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.98,0:02:19.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, Japan is suffering from issues like declining birthrates and class stratification.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.70,0:02:22.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, when I see the fine young people lined up before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:25.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can only see a bright future before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:29.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that Japan is still in good shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.78,0:02:31.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It brings a smile to my face.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:35.80,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today must be a good day for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:43.30,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if today will be mellow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:49.02,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Ryuugamine Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.02,0:02:52.10,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A shy boy that just recently came to Tokyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.10,0:02:54.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Sonohara Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.40,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:03:00.95,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl that gives off the feeling of naivety...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kida Masaomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.31,0:03:07.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite looking a bit mature,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:12.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm actually a fragile, easily hurt fifteen-year-old kid like all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:14.84,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy that lives in his own saccharine dreamworld...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kamichika Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.73,0:03:18.72,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.72,0:03:21.76,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl with an enigmatic past...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:25.93,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,They're people you'd see on the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:27.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harima...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.29,0:03:30.43,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Harima Mika here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Absent...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:39.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A mundane, familiar scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.46,0:03:43.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice going on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.86,0:03:45.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were introducing ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:47.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can introduce yourself from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.41,0:03:49.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yagiri Seiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.89,0:03:51.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet all of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:55.77,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,However, there are unexpected moments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.77,0:04:01.12,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,when reality shows its other face.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.12,0:04:05.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your seat, Yagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:05.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:10.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be able to come to school for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.84,0:04:13.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, perhaps I'll never come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.81,0:04:16.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just stopped by to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.90,0:04:18.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:22.34,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yagiri, what's the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:25.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.08,0:04:29.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take care of something very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.31,0:04:32.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't deal with you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.61,0:04:34.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, Yagiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:36.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:38.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:43.59,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,A sudden crack in the peaceful life disturbs the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:48.60,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And we have a girl who took a peek at that crack.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.60,0:04:53.18,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, she was supposed to be dead two days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:05:00.73,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She was born in a normal household.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.22,0:05:04.49,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She lived a life without any problems or poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:11.37,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,However, when she entered middle school,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.41,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,an envelope was sent to her, like an ambush.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was in the envelope?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.75,0:05:24.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.60,0:05:26.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like my dad's having an affair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:28.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's seeing another woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.97,0:05:30.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there was a letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.63,0:05:33.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Could you forgive him?" it asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.84,0:05:37.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the person who sent the letter is somehow related to that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:39.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, your father isn't completely innocent,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.65,0:05:41.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but neither is the one who sent the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:47.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so perplexed that I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:50.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to hide the envelope for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.24,0:05:52.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since then,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:57.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became disgusted with the normal atmosphere in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:00.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was hard, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Rio?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:05.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could only endure it for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.20,0:06:09.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everything would get better if I confronted him about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:16.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to talk about it if it's too hard for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:20.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I don't want to share with others too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.90,0:06:21.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.12,0:06:23.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:30.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I thought the TV remote was my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:30.08,Drrr Override,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. That was silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:37.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure if my mother had decided not to bring it up, or if they'd discussed it before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:42.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both my father's lame jokes, and the overly sweet taste of my mother's stew...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing had changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.26,0:06:52.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought, "I should disappear to cause a change."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.56,0:06:59.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(2983,3984,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}Lately, my mind has been full of such thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:04.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a situation like yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:07.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as serious as yours though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.89,0:07:09.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a girl I was going out with,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.27,0:07:14.57,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she was impregnated by my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.77,0:07:19.12,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the person I absolutely couldn't forgive was my mother. {well couldnt forgive most}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.58,0:07:23.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it happens all the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:26.71,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that we have a reputation to protect, so we shouldn't make a fuss about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:29.99,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She didn't say anything about how she felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.99,0:07:35.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought she cared more about our reputation than about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:40.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe she was thinking about my future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:42.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:43.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't thinking about you at all, Nakura-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.19,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just selfish! Only thinking about herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.14,0:07:52.65,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.65,0:07:53.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.22,0:08:02.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Magenta-san, will you disappear with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:05.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If both of us die,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.74,0:08:08.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure they'd finally realize...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:12.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what they should have cherished.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:17.86,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,In retrospect, it was a pretty foolish decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.86,0:08:20.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But she left the house with determination.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.15,0:08:24.14,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She felt some strength in Nakura's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.14,0:08:29.68,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She wanted to see the person who shared her thoughts with her own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:35.65,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it had been a lie, she had nothing to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.65,0:08:36.79,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Or so she thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.00,0:08:43.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.61,0:08:44.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magenta-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:46.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.13,0:08:48.44,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Nakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.44,0:08:51.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I knew it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.94,0:08:51.74,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,When she saw him, she thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.13,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.74,0:08:54.13,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,"Is this man really Nakura?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:56.83,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:08:57.63,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She followed him
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.83,0:08:58.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.63,0:09:01.39,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,because she wouldn't forgive herself if she ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:00.91,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:16.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,So, even if this happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.43,0:09:17.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone around?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.28,0:09:23.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.67,0:09:25.00,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:26.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for tricking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.63,0:09:28.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Various emotions such as fear, regret, and resistance
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:31.09,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,were juxtaposed in her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:34.64,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,but before she lost consciousness, she thought,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.67,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,"This must be my fate."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.67,0:09:40.97,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there really any reason to care about herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.97,0:09:43.35,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She would just vanish from this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.94,0:09:46.32,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,without anyone noticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:48.27,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone {\i1}is{\i0}{\fscx170} {\fscx100}around.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.20,0:10:12.38,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when she was unconscious, the world kept revolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:16.67,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's not really a hard job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.02,0:10:20.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.94,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Her feelings and will were irrelevant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.20,0:10:56.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:59.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just couldn't get the money together.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.63,0:11:01.58,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying that I can't pay it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.58,0:11:03.49,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if something were to happen to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:06.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiki-san from the Awakusu group wouldn't stay quiet—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:07.85,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.85,0:11:09.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I'm busy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.93,0:11:15.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the time that I'll waste on you is just two and a half minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.07,0:11:20.47,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the other guy you shouldn't piss off is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:34.59,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:39.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it's necessary to tell an excellent transporter like you how to do it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.93,0:11:42.11,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you don't need to do more than I've asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:45.60,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just smack some sense into them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.21,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The world is revolving.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.21,0:11:56.08,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Things were going a bit astray from the "fate" the girl believed in.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.08,0:11:57.21,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:21.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the fuck are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:06.54,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It read, "I've been asked to bring you to a certain place."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.36,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The bike moved silently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.43,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes it neighed like a horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.43,0:13:15.41,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:20.81,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet this empty feeling was real.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.72,0:13:25.55,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl wondered what lay beyond that warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:30.16,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What were that person's thoughts? What did they know? How did they live?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.16,0:13:33.87,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,How did she appear to that person?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.28,0:13:41.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:34.26,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magenta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you. I'm Nakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.98,0:14:44.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really Nakura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Correct. The Nakura who wants to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really delighted to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.93,0:14:55.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you save me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:57.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:14:59.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.41,0:15:00.87,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.55,0:15:02.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:04.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must have felt terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:05.33,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:08.42,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know I'd been kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.42,0:15:13.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, because I asked them to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:17.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was also me who saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:23.84,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were suicidal, but you got kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:29.08,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you were a bit frustrated at yourself for getting scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.08,0:15:32.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you'd resisted, it'd mean that you'd denied the you that wanted to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.54,0:15:36.73,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you just accepted the events, forcing yourself to believe it was your fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:40.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now that you've been rescued, you feel relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:43.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to see that expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.42,0:15:46.86,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.86,0:15:50.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see your dumbfounded face when someone saw through you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.28,0:15:55.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good question.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.51,0:16:01.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I believe the answer might sound quite philosophical to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:04.09,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. If I had to explain it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.09,0:16:06.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I like humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:08.97,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are so interesting and amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.97,0:16:10.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just can't help myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:14.03,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, to make it clear, I just like humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:15.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean you in particular.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.53,0:16:17.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.04,0:16:22.45,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.45,0:16:25.04,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you finally realized your place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:26.50,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.82,0:16:37.94,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a few people have jumped from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.94,0:16:40.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not enough to make this place famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:43.18,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if you jump from here, your death is certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.18,0:16:45.31,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that stain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:56.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, don't you think you're special?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:58.54,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.54,0:17:00.61,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.61,0:17:07.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one in the world can live honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:12.17,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even you have a secret or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:16.63,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you ever wondered why you're so perfect while your parents are so pathetic?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.64,0:17:21.88,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I came to a conclusion...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.88,0:17:26.64,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The show goes on, and everyone laughs at lame jokes or eats overly sweet stew,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.64,0:17:29.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,regardless of whether they're having an affair or whether their wife knows about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:35.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.35,0:17:38.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite all their worries, they're all bloodstains adorning the pavement now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:40.70,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing more. Without exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:44.30,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All are equal in front of the Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.22,0:17:46.96,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I let go of your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:55.46,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.13,0:17:58.68,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.08,0:18:05.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to see your ugly feelings today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.77,0:18:09.39,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really interested in your problems,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.39,0:18:12.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in the way you live when they stress you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.05,0:18:15.90,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and you were awfully boring. Your life was just as I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:19.15,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew from the beginning that you weren't serious about dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:20.41,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.41,0:18:23.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun, Magenta-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.13,0:18:39.56,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She hesitated for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.56,0:18:44.77,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Would she be able to hurt him if she jumped?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.42,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But then she thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.42,0:18:50.98,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'd just been waiting for the opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:55.07,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And that opportunity came from that man's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.35,0:19:01.92,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,But without being aware...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.94,0:19:33.77,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.15,0:19:38.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:57.29,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh, acting on your own again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.04,0:20:06.14,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she thought about her parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:08.12,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Her dad and his lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.12,0:20:09.03,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Her dad and her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:13.27,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And she also thought about the times she didn't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:20.39,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they weren't as wicked, selfish, and hate-filled as she thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.16,0:20:25.53,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps they weren't veiled by her own weakness and compromises.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.17,0:20:27.53,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,As she tried to find her way back home,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:31.68,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\t(2728,3689,\c&H000000&\3c&H000000&\4c&H000000&)}she thought about forgiving them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.23,0:20:37.75,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since that day, the world has appeared completely different to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:41.50,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,There are as many feelings and secrets as there are people.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.88,0:20:45.05,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,She realized that it was very normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:46.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do ya wanna go?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:49.32,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you anywhere, so uh, treat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.32,0:20:50.62,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.62,0:20:52.52,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about a bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:55.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there are a lot of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:21:00.28,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Even these two normal school boys have their secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.57,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Feelings they can't share with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.75,0:21:05.07,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.07,0:21:08.20,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagiri-kun, what's bothering you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.20,0:21:09.28,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:13.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can't skip school on the first day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.24,0:21:14.78,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.78,0:21:15.56,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:16.79,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.16,0:21:18.25,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:24.53,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.35,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such a lady-killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:30.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl with glasses has fallen head over heels for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:35.92,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could see her anxiety about the dangerous and risky days awaiting her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.92,0:21:37.98,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mind translating that into Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:39.98,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And he...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:41.98,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And she...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:45.26,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,What they see might not always be reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.26,0:21:46.84,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, she started to ponder...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:50.69,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,Will a day come when she can say those words to someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.24,0:21:56.27,Drrr Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,"Because the world isn't as cruel as you think it is."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.52,0:22:05.51,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you became a Champion of Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:13.01,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I asked an excellent transporter...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:17.76,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.76,0:22:21.69,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, Orihara Izaya, a mere informant, isn't that relentless.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.40,0:22:28.24,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not nice enough to stop anyone who wants to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:35.74,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fun, excellent transporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.38,0:24:16.05,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikebukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.75,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He, she, me, and you...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.75,0:24:19.93,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We came here searching for something,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.93,0:24:20.89,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,seeking something,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.89,0:24:24.23,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to change something.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.23,0:24:25.81,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Rampant.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.81,0:24:27.27,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want some sushi? It's yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.27,0:24:30.38,Drrr Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mister, long time no see.
